Text
Girikha,

I have prayed at your shrine, and left this there, in the hopes of my
prayers reaching Your ears.  

I hesitate to seek you in this fashion--I have long been an applicant to the
Champions, seeking to serve alongside them, but only recently have I begun
to think it might be possible for me to fight for you as well without
dishonor.  Rakhrhun Chakkach suggested to me that I seek your favor, despite
my admission that I had sought the Champions out, and I chose to accept the
