Subject A research project.~
Text
My friend, I hope this missive finds you in good health and sound mind. 
Recently while visiting the spirit palace I came across an old history book.
The book detailed the founding of the spirit tower and some of the trials
the first Arch-mages had known.  For the most part this proved to be a
rather boring read, there is however one section of history that caught my
attention.  During the reign of the fight Arch-mage a group of scholars
splintered off from the traditional guilds and formed what the Spirit mages
called a cult.  This group of scholars called themselves the Maevis'Hra and
theiy used a fusion of fire and void magic in an attempt to bring an eternal
night to Avendar.  Supposedly this group is responsible for bringing the
demon lord Kzroth into the realms, if that is true then they wielded awesome
power indeed.  

I request that you use whatever texts or resources that you have available
to research this group and their quest for power.  You will of course be
reimbursed for your time, when we next meet if you decide to research this
for me we can discuss a price.  Personally I think we could both benefit
from the knowledge this group may have collected.  If void and fire could be
fused why not other spheres or even the combination of your musical magic
and the arcane.  The possibilities are endless, as is the potential for
power.  

Think about it and let me know, I await your reply and your expertise.  

Archmage Torai Realor 
